  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT26">
<l>maṟṟut toḻuvā roruvaraiyum yāṉiṉmai</l>
<l>kaṟṟaic caṭaiyāṉ karikaṇṭā yeṟṟaikkuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṭukoḷ kaṇṭāy kaṭalvaṇṇā yāṉuṉṉaik</l>
<l>kaṇṭukoḷ kiṟkumā ṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See! [Śiva] with tied-up matted locks is witness</l>
<l>to the fact that I do not have any other [deities] to worship.</l>
<l>O sea-hued [Lord]! Look, see to it that</l>
<l>I am able to learn about [You] forever!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
